# Where should we write the GIF?
Output demo_tab_completion_easing.gif

Source demo_settings.tape
Set Height 500
Source demo_setup.tape

Type "flyline set-cursor --interpolate-easing "
Sleep 500ms
Tab
Sleep 2500ms
Type "out"
Sleep 1500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

Sleep 2s
